                                          <div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
                                             <div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
                                                <h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Our Approach</span></h4>
                                                <div class="et_pb_blurb_description">
                                                   <div>We believe that before starting the proper treatment for a patient regarding any disease or disorder, it is very important to examine his or her symptoms in an Ayurvedic way. For this purpose, we assign with you a dedicated health consultant who understands your problems and symptoms deeply. This involves a lot of questions and answers sessions between the counselor and the patient. We always encourage the patients to give the correct information regarding their health status for correct treatment. </div>
