                                             <div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
                                                <h4 class="et_pb_module_header"><span>Our Process</span></h4>
                                                <div class="et_pb_blurb_description">
                                                   <div>The health status and treatment of a patient is not decided by a single consultant, rather a team of consultants start to look into the reports of the patient and then a unanimous decision is taken by the team regarding the course of the treatment. The treatment process is always initiated through the Ayurvedic System of Medicine. This involves prescribing approved herbal compositions, classical or proprietary tablets, ointments etc. This process is always different with people with different symptoms.</div>
                                                   <div></div>
                                                </div>
